~ task2_ready_or_repeat
do Character.play_audio("task2_ready")
=>< snippets/focus_conversation
Sam: Are you ready to move our ship to Planet Stardust? Remember, we have to copy the words AND match the highs and lows of the special phrase to steer our ship. Let your Captain know if you are ready or if you would like to hear the examples again. [next=10]
# experimenter will decide if participant needs to loop back to 1st bad imitation example

System: ...
