~ task2_stimuli
#12 Phrases – 6 song, 6 speech randomized (see list of sentences on last page)*
System: Select stimuli order
- Order A
	=>< orders/A
- Order B
	=>< orders/B
- Order C
	=>< orders/C
- Order D
	=>< orders/D
- Skip to success. 
	=> task2_success


~ task2_stimuli_trial
=>< snippets/focus_screen
# loop through stimuli
while stimuli_set.size() > 0
	set flying_motion = 0.4
	set next_stimuli = stimuli_set.pop_front()
	System:
	- Begin {{next_stimuli}}
	set screen = "talking"
	do Stimuli.play(next_stimuli)
	do Recorder.start()
	[next=2]
